Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:50.94,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(762,144)}『百鬼夜行』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:50.94,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,310)}教师点评
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:50.94,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(596,201)}正确。 不愧是姬路同学。
